The 'Beat 'em up' tag on Steam signifies games that fall under the genre of action where players engage in combat against hordes of enemies in a continuous fashion. These games typically feature hand-to-hand or melee combat, and the gameplay often emphasizes combos, agility, and quick reflexes. Developers and community members on Steam apply this tag to games that fit this description, ensuring users can easily discover and explore titles within the genre.
